  (46, 'Limited Edition — Cap Collection', 'limited-edition-cap-collection-46', 'Exclusive cap design not available in standard catalog. Embroidered logo, adjustable strap. Once sold out, will not be restocked.', 200, 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1546868871-7041f69a55b0?w=600&h=600&fit=crop', 9, '2026-07-02T13:02:30.294Z'),
